{"tid":9774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得煲水式熱水爐好唔人道，應該立法禁止使用？","createTime":"2016-11-28T16:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T06:18:59.000Z","uid":36366,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3701723d2ed4c54a22eba04cf0b133cd3e34269","tid":9774,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:46:57.000Z","msg":"我老豆比人水左佢買部煲水式熱水爐<br />\n係夏天條撚樣係我屋企沖左十分鐘涼出黎同我講無野，沖到巢哂皮都係熱，我老豆又聽佢水<br />\n而家冬天，煲成四個字沖得五分鐘都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡直係慘無人道<br />\n<br />\n正皮：支持立法<br />\n負皮：關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"a46b72c823e5910a59eb4ca1eab6477bb03cf44e","tid":9774,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"鍛煉意志力呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7a0ce2c3b7f7bd08d19f9b331c33f9411d6a46","tid":9774,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:49:12.000Z","msg":"都唔知邊撚個諗電熱式熱水爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cb42ac3fab3b960defe90bca6df4033847dbb7","tid":9774,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍛煉意志力呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f188630999912bd861c790f3ec3d30e05cf4b551","tid":9774,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:52:30.000Z","msg":"當個衰仔話沖完涼重有熱水果時，我就知佢沖得越黎越快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ea359051c02b73f20cacf5129e3ed9d5c8a4e7","tid":9774,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鍛煉意志力呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n禁錯制，用唔慣新app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔小心沖耐左就洗唔到頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.